title: #14 - Dillon Francis On Crazy Tour Stories & Music Collab with CouRage
itunes:title: #14 - Dillon Francis On Crazy Tour Stories & Music Collab with CouRage
description: On this episode of The CouRage and Nadeshot Show presented by Cash App, CouRage and Nadeshot welcome on electronic music artist, Dillon Francis. They discuss his crazy tour stories, his love for Call of Duty, his pinata mascot Gerald, and more.
